 <section id="cost" class="mb-12">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-4">4. Cost Comparison</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">While GaN V chargers carry a 20-35% unit cost premium over silicon equivalents, the total cost of ownership often favors GaN V when shipping, returns, and brand positioning are factored in. The table below summarizes the key differences between silicon and GaN V chargers for OEM/ODM buyers:</p>
