 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">For OEM/ODM buyers, the consumer electronics segment offers the fastest return on investment due to higher volumes and shorter product cycles. GaN V chargers in the 65W-140W range are currently the most popular configurations, providing an optimal balance of performance, size, and manufacturing cost. WOWOHCOOL offers reference designs across all power levels that can be customized with your branding, packaging, and charging specifications within 25-30 days from sample approval, with dedicated project management from concept through delivery.</p>
 </section>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">As GaN V technology matures and production scales, the cost premium over traditional silicon chargers continues to narrow. Industry analysts project that GaN V chargers will reach price parity with silicon by 2027, making now the ideal time for brands to invest in GaN V product development and establish a foothold in the next generation of charging technology.</p>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">According to the USB Implementers Forum (USB-IF), over 4 billion USB-C devices have been shipped globally, with PD 3.1 adoption growing 50% year-over-year. This massive installed base creates enormous demand for high-quality GaN V chargers that can deliver the full benefits of USB-C fast charging across multiple device categories.</p>
